For people looking at the answer in the future:
1. Ensure package is properly imported

2. Ensure Semantic JSX attribute has state properly inputted

3. Ensure state is properly set

4. Try changing the css class setting between _class_ and _className_

5. Lastly, try setting other elements with the state variable, it&#39;s highly possible for whatever reason semantic won&#39;t allow certain variables to be set with certain elements

6. If all else fails, change the native css for semantic UI

